  3 important terms in JAVA:
  ------------------------------
  JVM[JAVA VIRTUAL MACHINE]-> engine that executes your code; Translator , Manager, Safety
  JRE[JAVA RUNTIME ENVIRONMENT]-> Executes Java bytecode natively
  JDK[JAVA DEVELOPMENT KIT]-> comprehensive software toolkit used to write, compile, debug, and run Java applications.

  TO COMPLIE JAVA PROGRAM :javac YourFileName.java
  TO RUN JAVA PROGRAM : java YourFileName

